author: @sabr9906
text: Cool, one tip:  chunkGram and chunkParser should be moved out from the loop.  for i in tokenized[5:]:             words = nltk.word_tokenize(i)             tagged = nltk.pos_tag(words)              chunkGram = r"""Chunk: {<.*>+}                                     }<VB.?|IN|DT|TO>+{"""             chunkParser = nltk.RegexpParser(chunkGram)              chunked = chunkParser.parse(tagged)             ...
